<br>
But what they didn't know was that as the Scynthian Queen made her way towards the village under the full moon, she was different.<br>
<br>
Alysia had been missing since the war and mysteriously appeared back in Scynthia a few days later. However, after a battle against the Priests of Poseidon, Alysia's headress was knocked off and there stood Gabrielle, Alysia's twin sister posing in her place.<br>
<br>
So where was Alysia? The Amazon Nation had pronounced her dead. But when the Priests of Poseidon and other enemies of Scynthia returned to take claim on the lands of Scynthia, there Alysia rose with bloodlust in her eyes. The word of the battle had spread across the lands faster than a plague. Alysia was alive. . . and kicking serious butt.<br>
<br>
She slowly walked into the village of Themiscrya, quiet and weary. She wore her usual short amazon leathers, but without her boots and weapons. <br>
<br>
In her eyes was a passion that had been lost long ago. But yet a curiousness within her soul. As if looking for answers. Belle had given her so many after she awoke in the Ancient Caves, but she needed more. And Belle said she could find some in Themiscrya, where Queen Hippolyte ruled.<br>
<br>
For she was no longer Alysia . . . but Samsara once again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 54<br> <font color=#993300>(1/18/02 8:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re:</span><hr size=1> ((wow....thats cool....i miss aly already lol)) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 289<br> <font color=#993300>(1/21/02 12:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Wandering</span><hr size=1> Alysia glanced about through the vilalge. It was quiet. She didn't like quiet.<br>
